Basic sinatra app setup with the capability to run on the OpenShift under ruby 1.9.3

Be sure to, at first, create the marker file at .openshift/markers/force_clean_build, otherwise the haml gem won't bundle properly.

Deploying on OpenShift:
rhc env set NODE_ENV=production -a $appname
rhc env set APP_SECRET_HASH='$your-secret-hash' -a $appname